<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

  <title>PO4OR Académie | Portail de l’Orient</title>

  <meta
    name="description"
    content="PO4OR Académie propose des formations, ateliers et programmes culturels, médiatiques et audiovisuels."
  >

  <style>
    :root {
      --red: #ed1c24;
      --red-dark: #c9141c;
      --blue: #194f80;
      --blue-dark: #102f50;
      --gold: #b6923d;
      --gold-light: #ddc27d;
      --grey: #68717b;
      --grey-dark: #303841;
      --grey-light: #f3f5f7;
      --white: #ffffff;
      --border: #e2e6ea;
      --shadow: 0 18px 45px rgba(16, 47, 80, 0.12);
      --radius: 22px;
      --container: 1180px;
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    html {
      scroll-behavior: smooth;
    }

    body {
      color: var(--grey-dark);
      background: var(--white);
      font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.65;
    }

    body.menu-open {
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    a {
      color: inherit;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    button,
    input,
    select,
    textarea {
      font: inherit;
    }

    .container {
      width: min(var(--container), calc(100% - 40px));
      margin-inline: auto;
    }

    /* Barre supérieure */

    .topbar {
      color: var(--white);
      background: var(--blue-dark);
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .topbar-inner {
      min-height: 38px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .topbar-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .topbar a:hover {
      color: var(--gold-light);
    }

    /* Navigation */

    .header {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 1000;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.96);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    }

    .header-inner {
      min-height: 96px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 30px;
    }

    .brand {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .brand-mark {
      padding-right: 18px;
      border-right: 1px solid var(--gold);
      line-height: 1;
    }

    .brand-mark small {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 7px;
      color: var(--grey);
      font-size: 9px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.25em;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .brand-mark strong {
      color: var(--red);
      font-family: Georgia, "Times New Roman", serif;
      font-size: 42px;
      font-weight: 400;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    }

    .academy-word {
      color: var(--gold);
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 0.26em;
    }

    .academy-subtitle {
      display: block;
      margin-top: 5px;
      color: var(--grey);
      font-size: 10px;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    }

    .navigation {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 25px;
      list-style: none;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .navigation a {
      transition: color 0.2s ease;
    }

    .navigation a:hover {
      color: var(--red);
    }

    .nav-button {
      padding: 12px 20px;
      color: var(--white) !important;
      background: var(--red);
      border-radius: 999px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(237, 28, 36, 0.22);
    }

    .nav-button:hover {
      background: var(--red-dark);
    }

    .menu-toggle {
      display: none;
      width: 46px;
      height: 46px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 50%;
      color: var(--blue-dark);
      background: var(--white);
      font-size: 23px;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    /* Hero */

    .hero {
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 88% 16%, rgba(182, 146, 61, 0.22), transparent 28%),
        linear-gradient(135deg, #ffffff 0%, #f6f8fa 66%, #edf2f5 100%);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .hero::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0 auto 0 0;
      width: 7px;
      background: linear-gradient(
        to bottom,
        var(--red) 0 33.33%,
        var(--gold) 33.33% 66.66%,
        var(--blue) 66.66% 100%
      );
    }

    .hero-inner {
      min-height: 650px;
      padding-block: 85px;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 0.9fr;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 70px;
    }

    .eyebrow {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 11px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      color: var(--blue);
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .eyebrow::before {
      content: "";
      width: 38px;
      height: 3px;
      background: var(--gold);
    }

    .hero h1 {
      color: var(--blue-dark);
      font-family: Georgia, "Times New Roman", serif;
      font-size: clamp(52px, 7vw, 88px);
      font-weight: 400;
      line-height: 0.98;
      letter-spacing: -0.045em;
    }

    .hero h1 span {
      display: block;
      margin-top: 18px;
      color: var(--red);
      font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.25em;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 0.34em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .hero-description {
      max-width: 680px;
      margin-top: 28px;
      color: var(--grey);
      font-size: 19px;
    }

    .hero-actions {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 14px;
      margin-top: 34px;
    }

    .button {
      min-height: 52px;
      padding: 0 25px;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      border: 1px solid transparent;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-weight: 800;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: 0.25s ease;
    }

    .button-primary {
      color: var(--white);
      background: var(--red);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 28px rgba(237, 28, 36, 0.20);
    }

    .button-primary:hover {
      background: var(--red-dark);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    .button-secondary {
      color: var(--blue);
      background: var(--white);
      border-color: var(--blue);
    }

    .button-secondary:hover {
      color: var(--white);
      background: var(--blue);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    .featured-card {
      position: relative;
      padding: 38px;
      background: var(--white);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 30px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }

    .featured-card::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      top: -1px;
      left: 38px;
      width: 95px;
      height: 5px;
      background: var(--gold);
    }

    .featured-label {
      color: var(--red);
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .featured-card h2 {
      margin: 16px 0;
      color: var(--blue-dark);
      font-family: Georgia, "Times New Roman", serif;
      font-size: 31px;
      line-height: 1.2;
    }

    .featured-card p {
      color: var(--grey);
    }

    .featured-list {
      margin-top: 22px;
      list-style: none;
    }

    .featured-list li {
      padding: 13px 0;
      display: flex;
      gap: 12px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .featured-list li:last-child {
      border-bottom: 0;
    }

    .featured-list li::before {
      content: "◆";
      margin-top: 4px;
      color: var(--gold);
      font-size: 10px;
    }

    /* Sections */

    section {
      padding-block: 95px;
    }

    .section-soft {
      background: var(--grey-light);
    }

    .section-header {
      max-width: 760px;
      margin-bottom: 46px;
    }

    .section-kicker {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      color: var(--red);
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 0.18em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .section-title {
      color: var(--blue-dark);
      font-family: Georgia, "Times New Roman", serif;
      font-size: clamp(38px, 5vw, 58px);
      font-weight: 400;
      line-height: 1.1;
    }

    .section-description {
      margin-top: 18px;
      color: var(--grey);
      font-size: 18px;
    }

    /* Programmes */

    .programmes-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 24px;
    }

    .programme-card {
      position: relative;
      min-height: 300px;
      padding: 30px;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: var(--white);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      transition: 0.25s ease;
    }

    .programme-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-7px);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }

    .programme-number {
      color: var(--gold);
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    }

    .programme-card h3 {
      margin: 24px 0 14px;
      color: var(--blue);
      font-family: Georgia, "Times New Roman", serif;
      font-size: 27px;
      line-height: 1.2;
    }

    .programme-card p {
      color: var(--grey);
    }

    .programme-tags {
      margin-top: 24px;
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 8px;
    }

    .programme-tags span {
      padding: 6px 10px;
      color: var(--grey-dark);
      background: var(--grey-light);
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    /* Mission */

    .mission-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 0.9fr 1.1fr;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 70px;
    }

    .mission-quote {
      padding: 44px;
      color: var(--white);
      background: var(--blue-dark);
      border-radius: 28px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }

    .mission-quote small {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
      color: var(--gold-light);
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 0.15em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .mission-quote p {
      font-family: Georgia, "Times New Roman", serif;
      font-size: 28px;
      line-height: 1.45;
    }

    .mission-items {
      display: grid;
      gap: 8px;
    }

    .mission-item {
      padding: 22px 0;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 54px 1fr;
      gap: 18px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .mission-item:last-child {
      border-bottom: 0;
    }

    .mission-icon {
      width: 54px;
      height: 54px;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      color: var(--white);
      background: var(--red);
      border-radius: 16px;
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .mission-item h3 {
      color: var(--blue);
      font-size: 18px;
    }

    .mission-item p {
      margin-top: 5px;
      color: var(--grey);
    }

    /* Inscription */

    .registration {
      color: var(--white);
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 90% 5%, rgba(221, 194, 125, 0.18), transparent 25%),
        linear-gradient(120deg, var(--blue-dark), var(--blue));
    }

    .registration-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 0.85fr 1.15fr;
      align-items: start;
      gap: 65px;
    }

    .registration .section-kicker {
      color: var(--gold-light);
    }

    .registration .section-title,
    .registration .section-description {
      color: var(--white);
    }

    .registration-form {
      padding: 32px;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 16px;
      color: var(--grey-dark);
      background: var(--white);
      border-radius: 25px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }

    .form-group {
      display: grid;
      gap: 7px;
    }

    .form-group.full {
      grid-column: 1 / -1;
    }

    .form-group label {
      color: var(--blue-dark);
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .form-group input,
    .form-group select,
    .form-group textarea {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 13px 14px;
      color: var(--grey-dark);
      background: var(--white);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 12px;
      outline: none;
    }

    .form-group input:focus,
    .form-group select:focus,
    .form-group textarea:focus {
      border-color: var(--blue);
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(25, 79, 128, 0.10);
    }

    .form-group textarea {
      min-height: 110px;
      resize: vertical;
    }

    .form-status {
      display: none;
      padding: 12px 14px;
      color: #175f37;
      background: #eaf8f0;
      border-radius: 10px;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    /* Footer */

    .footer {
      padding: 56px 0 25px;
      color: #dce2e8;
      background: #242b32;
    }

    .footer-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.4fr 0.8fr 0.8fr;
      gap: 55px;
    }

    .footer h3 {
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      color: var(--white);
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    .footer p,
    .footer a {
      color: #b9c1c9;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .footer a:hover {
      color: var(--gold-light);
    }

    .footer-links {
      display: grid;
      gap: 9px;
    }

    .footer-bottom {
      margin-top: 44px;
      padding-top: 20px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.10);
      color: #939da7;
      font-size: 12px;
    }

    /* Responsive */

    @media (max-width: 980px) {
      .navigation {
        position: fixed;
        inset: 97px 0 auto 0;
        padding: 30px 20px 40px;
        display: none;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: stretch;
        background: var(--white);
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
        box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      }

      .navigation.open {
        display: flex;
      }

      .navigation a {
        display: block;
        padding: 11px 0;
      }

      .nav-button {
        text-align: center;
      }

      .menu-toggle {
        display: grid;
        place-items: center;
      }

      .hero-inner,
      .mission-grid,
      .registration-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .hero-inner {
        gap: 45px;
      }

      .programmes-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      }

      .footer-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 680px) {
      .topbar {
        display: none;
      }

      .header-inner {
        min-height: 84px;
      }

      .navigation {
        inset: 84px 0 auto 0;
      }

      .brand-mark strong {
        font-size: 34px;
      }

      .academy-name {
        display: none;
      }

      .hero-inner {
        min-height: auto;
        padding-block: 65px;
      }

      .hero h1 {
        font-size: 49px;
      }

      section {
        padding-block: 72px;
      }

      .programmes-grid,
      .registration-form,
      .footer-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .featured-card,
      .mission-quote,
      .registration-form {
        padding: 26px;
      }

      .form-group.full {
        grid-column: auto;
      }

      .footer-bottom {
        flex-direction: column;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="topbar">
    <div class="container topbar-inner">
      <span>Association culturelle · Paris</span>

      <div class="topbar-links">
        <a href="#programmes">Nos programmes</a>
        <a href="#inscription">Candidature</a>
        <a href="mailto:info@po4or.org">info@po4or.org</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <header class="header">
    <div class="container header-inner">
      <a class="brand" href="#accueil" aria-label="PO4OR Académie">
        <div class="brand-mark">
          <small>PORTAIL DE L’ORIENT</small>
          <strong>PO4OR</strong>
        </div>

        <div class="academy-name">
          ACADÉMIE
          <span class="academy-subtitle">FORMATIONS &amp; ATELIERS</span>
        </div>
      </a>

      <button
        class="menu-toggle"
        type="button"
        aria-label="Ouvrir le menu"
        aria-expanded="false"
      >
        ☰
      </button>

      <nav aria-label="Navigation principale">
        <ul class="navigation">
          <li><a href="#accueil">Accueil</a></li>
          <li><a href="#programmes">Programmes</a></li>
          <li><a href="#mission">Notre mission</a></li>
          <li><a href="#publics">Publics</a></li>
          <li><a class="nav-button" href="#inscription">S’inscrire</a></li>
        </ul>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main>
    <section class="hero" id="accueil">
      <div class="container hero-inner">
        <div>
          <span class="eyebrow">Apprendre · Créer · Transmettre</span>

          <h1>
            PO4OR
            <span>Académie</span>
          </h1>

          <p class="hero-description">
            Une plateforme de formations et d’ateliers portée par
            l’association Portail de l’Orient, au service des jeunes,
            des talents émergents et des porteurs de projets culturels.
          </p>

          <div class="hero-actions">
            <a class="button button-primary" href="#programmes">
              Découvrir les programmes
            </a>

            <a class="button button-secondary" href="#inscription">
              Déposer une candidature
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <aside class="featured-card">
          <span class="featured-label">Programme annuel</span>

          <h2>Médias culturels et cinéma court</h2>

          <p>
            Un parcours gratuit associant apprentissage, pratique,
            accompagnement et création d’œuvres.
          </p>

          <ul class="featured-list">
            <li>Ateliers encadrés par des professionnels</li>
            <li>Formation à la narration et à l’image</li>
            <li>Production de projets individuels et collectifs</li>
            <li>Présentation publique des réalisations</li>
          </ul>
        </aside>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section-soft" id="programmes">
      <div class="container">
        <header class="section-header">
          <span class="section-kicker">Nos domaines</span>

          <h2 class="section-title">
            Des programmes conçus pour passer de l’idée à la création
          </h2>

          <p class="section-description">
            Des parcours accessibles, pratiques et progressifs,
            adaptés aux réalités du secteur culturel et créatif.
          </p>
        </header>

        <div class="programmes-grid">
          <article class="programme-card">
            <span class="programme-number">PROGRAMME 01</span>
            <h3>Médias culturels</h3>
            <p>
              Écriture éditoriale, reportage, entretien, vérification
              de l’information et publication numérique.
            </p>
            <div class="programme-tags">
              <span>Écriture</span>
              <span>Journalisme</span>
              <span>Publication</span>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="programme-card">
            <span class="programme-number">PROGRAMME 02</span>
            <h3>Cinéma court</h3>
            <p>
              Développement d’un projet, scénario, réalisation,
              tournage, montage et préparation à la diffusion.
            </p>
            <div class="programme-tags">
              <span>Scénario</span>
              <span>Réalisation</span>
              <span>Montage</span>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="programme-card">
            <span class="programme-number">PROGRAMME 03</span>
            <h3>Création numérique</h3>
            <p>
              Identité visuelle, communication digitale, contenus
              sociaux et outils numériques pour les projets culturels.
            </p>
            <div class="programme-tags">
              <span>Design</span>
              <span>Réseaux</span>
              <span>Communication</span>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="programme-card">
            <span class="programme-number">PROGRAMME 04</span>
            <h3>Écriture et narration</h3>
            <p>
              Transformer une expérience, une mémoire ou une idée
              en récit structuré et destiné à un public.
            </p>
            <div class="programme-tags">
              <span>Récit</span>
              <span>Podcast</span>
              <span>Storytelling</span>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="programme-card">
            <span class="programme-number">PROGRAMME 05</span>
            <h3>Production audiovisuelle</h3>
            <p>
              Préparation, organisation, budget, équipe,
              droits et suivi d’une production audiovisuelle.
            </p>
            <div class="programme-tags">
              <span>Production</span>
              <span>Budget</span>
              <span>Organisation</span>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="programme-card">
            <span class="programme-number">PROGRAMME 06</span>
            <h3>Ateliers artistiques</h3>
            <p>
              Des rencontres ponctuelles consacrées à la photographie,
              au son, à la scène et aux pratiques contemporaines.
            </p>
            <div class="programme-tags">
              <span>Art</span>
              <span>Image</span>
              <span>Expression</span>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="mission">
      <div class="container mission-grid">
        <div class="mission-quote">
          <small>Notre engagement</small>
          <p>
            Donner à chacun les moyens de raconter, de créer
            et de prendre sa place dans l’espace culturel.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mission-items">
          <article class="mission-item">
            <div class="mission-icon">01</div>
            <div>
              <h3>Une pédagogie concrète</h3>
              <p>
